{
  "texts": [
    "In the case studies of the previous section the NLP model was used without any adaptation to the text data at hand.",
    "For the task at hand, the results are already very good.",
    "However, in certain situations it might be required to further improve model performance.",
    "In this section we explore two approaches to how to fine-tune a transformer model:",
    "• Domain-specific fine-tuning involves updating the parameters of the transformer model using text data that is relevant to the domain where the model will be applied."
  ]
}